import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react";
import Button from "react-bootstrap/Button";
import Col from "react-bootstrap/Col";
import Form from "react-bootstrap/Form";
import Row from "react-bootstrap/Row";
function CreateIssue() {
  return (
    <Form>
      <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridState">
        <Form.Label>Project</Form.Label>
        <Form.Select defaultValue="Choose...">
          <option>mps</option>
          <option>broker</option>
          <option>Basidia</option>
        </Form.Select>
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridState">
        <Form.Label>Sprint</Form.Label>
        <Form.Select defaultValue="Choose...">
          <option>19112023</option>
          <option>19112024</option>
          <option>19112025</option>
          <option>19112026</option>
        </Form.Select>
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridState">
        <Form.Label>Status</Form.Label>
        <Form.Select defaultValue="Choose...">
          <option>TO DO</option>
          <option>IN PROGRESS</option>
          <option>DEV</option>
          <option>DONE</option>
        </Form.Select>
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridState">
        <Form.Label>Assigne</Form.Label>
        <Form.Select defaultValue="Choose...">
          <option>abc</option>
          <option>qwe</option>
          <option>xyz</option>
        </Form.Select>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridState">
        <Form.Label>Labels</Form.Label>
        <Form.Select defaultValue="Choose...">
          <option>Choose...</option>
          <option>...</option>
        </Form.Select>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridState">
        <Form.Label>Linked Issue</Form.Label>
        <Form.Select defaultValue="Choose...">
          <option>block</option>
          <option>is blocked by</option>
          <option>Relates To</option>
        </Form.Select>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="formGridState">
        <Form.Label>Selected Tickets</Form.Label>
        <Form.Select defaultValue="Choose...">
          <option>##1223444</option>
          <option>##1223444</option>
          <option>##1223444</option>
          <option>##1223444</option>
          <option>##1223444</option>
        </Form.Select>
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group controlId="formFileMultiple" className="mb-3">
        <Form.Label>Attachment</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control type="file" multiple />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="formGridAddress1">
        <Form.Label>Summary</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control placeholder="1234 Main St" />
      </Form.Group>
      <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlTextarea1">
        <Form.Label>Description</Form.Label>
        <Form.Control as="textarea" rows={3} />
      </Form.Group>

      <Form.Group as={Row} className="mb-3">
        <Col sm={{ span: 10, offset: 2 }}>
          <Button type="submit">Sign in</Button>
        </Col>
      </Form.Group>
    </Form>
  );
}
export default CreateIssue;
